review_text: Beautiful park, good to bring the kids to play with bike or skating
A small good place with beautiful trees and shrubs for walking. Can be improved with better care.It lacks flowering plants . Also some small fountains can be installed to add attraction.
A great place to walk and sit. There are picnic tables too. Got a lot of benches to sit
Clean and beautiful park in the côtes des neiges district.
Benches are all around the park to sit.
Cool calm place ,not a big park but it's good to relax , there are some area for kids to play and you can park your car on the side ,bus stop just in front of the park.
Nice place to go to play with children,

(Translated by Google) It is secluded and green.
We did not see any toys for the children.
You have to come by bus 161.
Its northeast corner is a vegetable garden, which is said to provide the municipality with families to grow tomatoes, cucumbers, vegetables, and so on. I know that much.

با اتوبوس ۱۶۱ باید آمد.
گوشۀ شمال‌‌شرقی‌اش باغچه‌های دنجی است که گفتند شهرداری در اختیار خانواده‌ها می‌گذارد تا گوجه و خیار و سبزی و... بکارند. در این حد می‌دانم.
